  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "張蒼，陽武人也，好書律曆。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "秦時為御史，主柱下方書。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "有罪，亡歸。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "及沛公略地過陽武，蒼以客從攻南陽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "蒼當斬，解衣伏質，身長大，肥白如瓠，時王陵見而怪其美士，乃言沛公，赦勿斬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "遂西入武關，至咸陽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "沛公立為漢王，入漢中，還定三秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "陳餘擊走常山王張耳，耳歸漢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "漢以蒼為常山守。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "從韓信擊趙，蒼得陳餘。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "趙地已平，漢王以蒼為代相，備邊冠。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "已而徙為趙相，相趙王耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "耳卒，相其子敖。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "復徙相代。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "燕王臧荼反，蒼以代相從攻荼有功，封為北平侯，食邑千二百戶。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "遷為計相，一月，更以列侯為主計四歲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "是時，蕭何為相國，而蒼乃自秦時為柱下御史，明習天下圖書計籍，又善用算律曆，故令蒼以列侯居相府，領主郡國上計者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "黥布反，漢立皇子長為淮南王，而蒼相之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "十四年，遷為御史大夫 〈(180 BCE)〉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "正月甲午，御史大夫北平侯張蒼為丞相 〈(176 BCE)〉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "張蒼亦學律歷，以為非是，罷之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "其後黃龍見成紀，張蒼自黜，所欲論著不成。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "而新垣平以望氣見，頗言正歷服色事，貴幸，後作亂，故孝文帝廢不復問。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "置陽陵邑。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "丞相北平侯張蒼卒 〈(151 BCE)〉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "周昌者，沛人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "其從兄苛，秦時皆為泗水卒史。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "及高祖起沛，擊破泗水守監，於是苛、昌以卒史從沛公，沛公以昌為職志，苛為客。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "從入關破秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "沛公立為漢王，以苛為御史大夫，昌為中尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "漢三年，楚圍漢王滎陽急，漢王出去，而使苛守滎陽城。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "楚破滎陽城，欲令苛將，苛罵曰：「若趣降漢王！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "不然，今為虜矣！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "項羽怒，亨苛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "漢王於是拜昌為御史大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "常從擊破項籍。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "六年，與蕭、曹等俱封，為汾陰侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "苛子成以父死事，封為高景侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "昌為人強力，敢直言，自蕭、曹等皆卑下之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "昌嘗燕入奏事，高帝方擁戚姬，昌還走。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "高帝逐得，騎昌項，上問曰：「我何如主也？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "昌仰曰：「陛下即桀、紂之主也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "於是上笑之，然尤憚昌。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "及高帝欲廢太子，而立威姬子如意為太子，大臣固爭莫能得，上以留侯策止。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "而昌庭爭之強，上問其說，昌為人吃，又盛怒，曰：「臣口不能言，然臣期期知其不可。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "陛下欲廢太子，臣期期不奉詔。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "上欣然而笑，即罷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "呂後側耳於東箱聽，見昌，為跪謝曰：「微君，太子幾廢。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "是歲，戚姬子如意為趙王，年十歲，高祖憂萬歲之後不全也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "趙堯為符璽御史，趙人方與公謂御史大夫周昌曰：「君之史趙堯年雖少，然奇士，君必異之，是且代君之位。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "昌笑曰：「堯年少，刀筆吏耳，何至是乎！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "居頃之，堯侍高祖，高祖獨心不樂，悲歌，群臣不知上所以然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "堯進請問曰：「陛下所為不樂，非以趙王年少，而戚夫人與呂後有隙，備萬歲之後而趙王不能自全乎？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "高祖曰：「我私憂之，不知所出。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "堯曰：「陛下獨為趙王置貴強相，及呂後、太子、群臣素所敬憚者乃可。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "高祖曰：「然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "吾念之欲如是，而群臣誰可者？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "堯曰：「御史大夫昌，其人堅忍伉直，自呂後、太子及大臣皆素嚴憚之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "獨昌可。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "高祖曰：「善。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "於是召昌謂曰：「吾固欲煩公，公強為我相趙。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "昌泣曰：「臣初起從陛下，陛下獨奈何中道而棄之于諸侯乎？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "高祖曰：「吾極知其左遷，然吾私憂趙，念非公無可者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "公不得已強行！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "於是徙御史大夫昌為趙相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "既行久之，高祖持御史大夫印弄之，曰：「誰可以為御史大夫者？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "孰視堯曰：「無以易堯。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "遂拜堯為御史大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "堯亦前有軍功食邑，及以御史大夫從擊陳豨有功，封為江邑侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "高祖崩，太后使使召趙王，其相昌令王稱疾不行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "使者三反，昌曰：「高帝屬臣趙王，王年少，竊聞太后怨戚夫人，欲召趙王並誅之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "臣不敢遣王，王且亦疾，不能奉詔。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "太后怒，乃使使召趙相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "相至，謁太后，太后罵昌曰：「爾不知我之怨戚氏乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "而不遣趙王！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "昌既被征，高後使使召趙王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "王果來，至長安月餘，見鴆殺。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "昌謝病不朝見，三歲而薨，諡曰悼侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "傳子至孫意，有罪，國除。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "景帝復封昌孫左車為安陽侯，有罪，國除。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "初，趙堯既代周昌為御史大夫，高祖崩，事惠帝終世。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "高後元年，怨堯前定趙王如意之畫，乃抵堯罪，以廣阿侯任敖為御史大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "初任敖免，平陽侯曹窋代敖為御史大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "高後崩，與大臣共誅諸呂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "後坐事免，以淮南相張蒼為御史大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "蒼來絳侯等尊立孝文皇帝，四年，代灌嬰為丞相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "漢興二十餘年，天下初定，公卿皆軍吏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "蒼為計相時，緒正律曆。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "以高祖十月始至霸上，故因秦時本十月為歲首，不革。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "推五德之運，以為漢當水德之時，上黑如故。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "吹律調樂，入之音聲，及以比定律令。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "若百工，天下作程品。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "至於為丞相，卒就之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "故漢家言律曆者本張蒼。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "蒼凡好書，無所不觀，無所不通，而尤邃律曆。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "蒼德安國侯王陵，及貴，父事陵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "陵死後，蒼為丞相，洗沐，常先朝陵夫人上食，然後敢歸家。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "初蒼父長不滿五尺，蒼長八尺餘，蒼子復長八尺，及孫類長六尺餘。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "蒼免相後，口中無齒，食乳，女子為乳母。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "妻妾以百數，嘗孕者不復幸。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "年百餘歲乃卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "著書十八篇，言陰陽律曆事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "申屠嘉",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "申屠嘉，梁人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "以材官蹶張從高帝擊項籍，遷為隊率。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "從擊黥布，為都尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "孝惠時，為淮陽守。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "孝文元年，舉故以二千石從高祖者，悉以為關內侯，食邑二十四人，而嘉食邑五百戶。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "十六年，遷為御史大夫。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "張蒼免相，文帝以皇后弟竇廣國賢有行，欲相之，曰：「恐天下以吾私廣國。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "久念不可，而高帝時大臣余見無可者，乃以御史大夫嘉為丞相，因故邑封為故安侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "嘉為人廉直，門不受私謁。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "是時，太中大夫鄧通方愛幸，賞賜累巨萬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "文帝常燕飲通家，其寵如是。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "是時，嘉入朝而通居上旁，有怠慢之禮。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "嘉奏事畢，因言曰：「陛下幸愛群臣則富貴之，至於朝廷之禮，不可以不肅！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "上曰：「君勿言，吾私之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "罷朝坐府中，嘉為檄召通詣丞相府，不來，且斬通。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "通恐，入言上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "上曰：「汝第往，吾今使人召若。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "通至丞相府，免冠，徒跣，頓首謝嘉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "嘉坐自如，弗為禮，責曰：「夫朝廷者，高皇帝之朝廷也，通小臣，戲殿上，大不敬，當斬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "史今行斬之！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "通頓首，首盡出血，不解。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "上度丞相已困通，使使持節召通，而謝丞相：「此語弄臣，君釋之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "鄧通既至，為上泣曰：「丞相幾殺臣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "嘉為丞相五歲，文帝崩，孝景即位。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "二年，晁錯為內史，貴幸用事，諸法令多所請變更，議以適罰侵削諸侯，而丞相嘉自絀所言不用，疾錯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "錯為內史，門東出，不便，更穿一門，南出。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "南出者，太上皇廟堧垣也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "嘉聞錯穿宗廟垣，為奏請誅錯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "客有語錯，錯恐，夜入宮上謁，自歸上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "至朝，嘉請誅內史錯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "上曰：「錯所穿非真廟垣，乃外堧垣，故冗官居其中，且又我使為之，錯無罪。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "罷朝，嘉謂長史曰：「吾悔不先斬錯乃請之，為錯所賣！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0136",
          "zh": "至舍，因嘔血而死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0137",
          "zh": "諡曰節侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0138",
          "zh": "傳子至孫臾，有罪，國除。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0139",
          "zh": "自嘉死後，開封侯陶青、桃侯劉舍及武帝時柏至侯許昌、平棘侯薛澤、武強侯莊青翟、商陵侯趙周，皆以列侯繼踵，娖娖廉謹，為丞相備員而已，無所能發明功名著於世者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0140",
          "zh": "贊曰：張蒼文好律曆，為漢名相，而專遵用奉之《顓頊曆》，何哉？",
          "translations": []
        },
        {
          "id": "s0141",
          "zh": "周昌，木強人也。",
          "translations": []
        },
        {
          "id": "s0142",
          "zh": "任敖以舊德用。",
          "translations": []
        },
        {
          "id": "s0143",
          "zh": "申屠嘉可謂剛毅守節，然無術學，殆與蕭、曹、陳平異矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
